songs.title: Do You Trust Me*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet
You want me to trust you
But how much do you trust me?
First off
This started when you broke in my phone
(Ayy, girl)

It doesn't really matter though
I feel like me and you girl, we had it all
I'm wishing on a star
Girl, tell me where you are
Or how you been
I'm gonna tell you now
We may never speak again
